Introduction

CrackShot is a South Korean Glam Rock band under OUI Entertainment, consisting of 4 members: Vincent, Willy K, Cyan and Danny Lee. The band debuted on October 12, 2015 with the digital single album Midnight Crime.

They’re well-known for being the winners of Superband 2. The members are currently under the five-member project rock band CraXilver.
